metaTitle: Mishra Jaati Teen Taal - Yogesh Samsi International Masterclass
metaDescription: The masterclass offers an in-depth exploration of Tabla solo performance, focusing on the fascinating rhythmic intricacies and advanced compositions within Mishra Jaati Teentaal. This is an opportunity to participate in an intensive workshop for talented young Tabla students by the world renowned Tabla player Yogesh Samsi, disciple of the late Ustad Allarakha and will be held on Saturday 12thJuly & Sunday 13th July 2025 via Zoom (Video conferencing & Webinar Platform).
title: Mishra Jaati Teen Taal
